@page
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Projects";
}

<section class="page-hero">
    <div class="section-heading">
        <p data-i18n-en="Projects" data-i18n-vi="Du an">Projects</p>
        <h2 data-i18n-en="Show real work with enough detail that people can judge your ability without guessing." data-i18n-vi="Trinh bay cong viec thuc te voi du chi tiet de moi nguoi co the danh gia nang luc cua ban ma khong can doan.">Show real work with enough detail that people can judge your ability without guessing.</h2>
    </div>
    <p class="page-lead" data-i18n-en="Replace these examples with your actual projects. The structure is already set up for portfolio case studies." data-i18n-vi="Hay thay cac vi du nay bang du an thuc te cua ban. Cau truc da duoc tao san de phu hop voi cac case study trong portfolio.">Replace these examples with your actual projects. The structure is already set up for portfolio case studies.</p>
</section>

<section class="section-shell">
    <div class="project-list project-list-stacked">
        <article class="project-card project-card-featured">
            <div class="project-copy">
                <span data-i18n-en="Featured project" data-i18n-vi="Du an noi bat">Featured project</span>
                <h3 data-i18n-en="Project Name One" data-i18n-vi="Ten du an mot">Project Name One</h3>
                <p data-i18n-en="Write a short case study here: what the product was, what problem it solved, what you were responsible for, and what made the build successful." data-i18n-vi="Viet mot case study ngan o day: san pham la gi, no giai quyet van de nao, ban phu trach nhung gi, va dieu gi lam nen thanh cong cua du an.">Write a short case study here: what the product was, what problem it solved, what you were responsible for, and what made the build successful.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li data-i18n-en="Role: design, frontend, backend, or full-stack" data-i18n-vi="Vai tro: design, frontend, backend hoac full-stack">Role: design, frontend, backend, or full-stack</li>
                    <li data-i18n-en="Stack: ASP.NET Core, JavaScript, SQL, or other tools" data-i18n-vi="Cong nghe: ASP.NET Core, JavaScript, SQL hoac cong cu khac">Stack: ASP.NET Core, JavaScript, SQL, or other tools</li>
                    <li data-i18n-en="Outcome: better UX, higher conversion, faster workflows, or stronger performance" data-i18n-vi="Ket qua: UX tot hon, chuyen doi cao hon, quy trinh nhanh hon hoac hieu nang tot hon">Outcome: better UX, higher conversion, faster workflows, or stronger performance</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="project-visual">
                <div class="visual-stack">
                    <div class="visual-card visual-card-large"></div>
                    <div class="visual-card visual-card-small"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="project-card">
            <div class="project-tag" data-i18n-en="Web app" data-i18n-vi="Web app">Web app</div>
            <h3 data-i18n-en="Project Name Two" data-i18n-vi="Ten du an hai">Project Name Two</h3>
            <p data-i18n-en="Describe the product, your contribution, and the specific quality of execution you want highlighted." data-i18n-vi="Mo ta san pham, dong gop cua ban va diem chat luong trien khai cu the ma ban muon lam noi bat.">Describe the product, your contribution, and the specific quality of execution you want highlighted.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="project-card">
            <div class="project-tag" data-i18n-en="Landing page" data-i18n-vi="Landing page">Landing page</div>
            <h3 data-i18n-en="Project Name Three" data-i18n-vi="Ten du an ba">Project Name Three</h3>
            <p data-i18n-en="Use this slot for a marketing or portfolio site that shows range in visual design and implementation." data-i18n-vi="Su dung muc nay cho mot website marketing hoac portfolio the hien duoc do rong trong thiet ke hinh anh va trien khai.">Use this slot for a marketing or portfolio site that shows range in visual design and implementation.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="project-card">
            <div class="project-tag" data-i18n-en="Dashboard" data-i18n-vi="Dashboard">Dashboard</div>
            <h3 data-i18n-en="Project Name Four" data-i18n-vi="Ten du an bon">Project Name Four</h3>
            <p data-i18n-en="Use this slot for a system-heavy interface with workflow, data display, and practical interaction design." data-i18n-vi="Su dung muc nay cho mot giao dien he thong co workflow, hien thi du lieu va thiet ke tuong tac thuc dung.">Use this slot for a system-heavy interface with workflow, data display, and practical interaction design.</p>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>
